      "title_align": "left",
      "order": 3,
      "alignment": "left",
      "body": "Three complementary views of viral lineage. **Pangolin / Nextclade bar charts** show classification frequencies. The **Sankey** traces each sample's path QC -> Pangolin lineage -> Nextclade clade; mismatched calls show up as crossing ribbons. The **PCA** clusters samples by their mutation profile - points are coloured by lineage, so well-defined lineage groups appear as distinct clusters.",
      "wf_tag": "nextflow/viralrecon"
    },
